title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight/map, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: Export the data from the table.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data from the table.
3. Observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
